"},{"pid":"7c08046557fd1972bcfa67fc2dc3880ab897b49b","tid":888723,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T07:03:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ed4179d72be36ebec8d1c2efdda164dcbc2dda","tid":888723,"uid":201356,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T07:06:49.000Z","msg":"多數唔會 自己手打已經預計好晒<br />\n未試過人打<br />\n<br />\n不過自己ff俾人㩒住侵犯嗰陣反而係咁喘到唞唔到氣捵床捵席蓆周身縮夾過電紅都面晒<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候好想呻吟下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f0a6a5047dfe8d3ce16fcdab9e8b7b922021de","tid":888723,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T07:07:07.000Z","msg":"淨係試過係屋企玩outlast嚇到大叫左出嚟,好彩得自己一個係屋企"},{"pid":"bd47380f1de67fc84a8e2834424fdd0439a253fe","tid":888723,"uid":23170,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T10:11:16.000Z","msg":"會呻吟嘅男仔最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823572bc4aeac7b058b39eaa5bdbbaf2f4dc3d5a","tid":888723,"uid":24311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T10:15:54.000Z","msg":"Coming coming"},{"pid":"7fb391535c616edaa8d8d2c1a5266c92f4f0a503","tid":888723,"uid":130303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5d1b8e99e08021f6176f5403348c71cb894025b","tid":888723,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T07:02:06.000Z","msg":"真心叫出黎會舒服d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下次冇人果時你可以試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:45:19.000Z","msg":"屋企長期有人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該試唔到了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114a8ee2b824fd7090fc9129bc2de6c0491a1b08","tid":888723,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T05:13:20.000Z","msg":"打飛機絕無意義　它不會扭轉屌閪的心意<br />\n夢遺是失去處子一首詩<br />\n<br />\n彷彿聽別人性事　今天我豈可打J多一次<br />\n打到條J刺痛一再開始<br />\n<br />\n＊到底想打飛機定睇AV 舊雲藏甜片也不再有意思<br />\n　誰要妳再說那吞精的句子<br />\n<br />\n到底想打飛機定睇AV　睡夢前欠缺了妳都不可以<br />\n　而這晚卻說我碌野 不可再次 啊！<br />\n<br />\n＃抽離從來不易　這個妳似蒼老師<br />\n　但到這夜方發覺　性與愛何幼稚<br />\n　若是熱烈做愛多一次　打J原來更易<br />\n　就算以後失去妳　仍笑說 打多次 人"},{"pid":"43b46368720d708c5daff2692365b4e8c5743267","tid":888723,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:21:12.000Z","msg":"睇到扯咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e49291cf1f9fe2bd6be63c889fa33f1a90e055ba","tid":888723,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2177775f20192dfd8786ba08fbdb7dbe16d06365","tid":888723,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:21:37.000Z","msg":"唔會"},{"pid":"7fb5426c46d955fde506713514d80b2f70399ff7","tid":888723,"uid":116330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:23:06.000Z","msg":"1069<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4149d7a3f40fb6464bee5e176e10402acb142acd","tid":888723,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fb5426c46d955fde506713514d80b2f70399ff7","tid":888723,"uid":116330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTim